// `core x = blocked (x + iterate cdround x @ 10)` from the reference
// `deps/cryptol-specs/.../chacha20.cry` reaches the chacha20 module's
// private `iterate` (`{a} (a -> a) -> a -> [inf]a`), which lowers to
// a SAWCore `Prelude.fix` over a spine ending in `Stream`, and the
// wrapped-scrutinee recursor convention refuses
// `Prelude::Stream@core` — the named diagnostic this row pins.
//
// This ChaCha20-shape stream comprehension is IN SCOPE long-term: the
// translation path (the `saw_self_ref_comp_iterate` parametric-bridge
// family / lazy selection) folds into the OP-3 successor design
// (doc/2026-07-12_obligation-placement-design.md §Instance 3,
// doc/2026-07-14_release-plan.md). Until that lands, translation must
// reject loudly rather than emit semantically different Lean. The
// retired success goldens live in git history (pre-2026-07-14) as the
// reference for what the row looked like when the pre-refactor
// translation path was live.

import "../../../../deps/cryptol-specs/Primitive/Symmetric/Cipher/Stream/chacha20.cry";

